href="erct-0014.xml"
title="Homotopy"
addr="erct-0014"
type="local">homotopy</fr:link> from <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[f\colon  A \to  A]]></fr:tex> onto the identity function. Then we may construct a higher homotopy from <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[H\circ  f]]></fr:tex> to <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathsf {act}_{f}\circ  H]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p>
 
   
